creditline: Gift of Elizabeth, Julie, and Catherine Andrus in memory of John and Marion Andrus

Signature, Date, Inscription

inscribed in plate at top: [GADITANAS COLVMNAS STATVIT HERCVLES]

inscribed on verso in graphite: C.30365 (code for Colnaghi, London)
provenance: P. & D. Colnaghi, London; John E. Andrus III, Wayzata, Minn.; by descent to his daughters, Elizabeth, Katie, and Julie. Earlier provenances have been gathered, but further research will increase our knowledge of their histories.

title: Hercules Carrying the Columns of Gaza, From the Labors of Hercules
